</h4></div><div><div class="blog-summary"><em>Ethel Rohan’s second novel, </em>Sing, I<em>, was published by TriQuarterly Books on April 15. The novel’s heroine, Ester Prynn, works in a…</em>
</div></div><span class="views-field views-field-field-date"><span class="field-content date-display-single">April 16, 2024
